/>\n唔同題型有唔同答法<br />\n唔中佢個答題框架寫幾多都冇用唔會高分<br />\n要不斷操試卷先得 起碼要大半年時間先熟習到<br />\n最後係寫字速度一定要夠快<br />\n卷一 兩個鐘做5題資料題 卷二一 個鐘三個字寫兩題essay<br />\n想自修嘅巴絲要諗清楚先好決定<br />\n如果你睇完覺得應付到嘅先再報啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 dse歷史lv5"},{"pid":"a6a7a0bef68cb29fa2ed9b71db0098b1c1bfd1c6","tid":588224,"uid":135179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48ff0d9ef59dfeecae2e1304e7ca5686d24e52bc","tid":588224,"uid":69140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"有frd話好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由零開始有冇可能5*"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"睇你有冇心<br />\n冇心比幾耐你都冇用"},{"pid":"b581e23906b3bed256273d33b79dd32c6443c28e","tid":588224,"uid":8353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"我淨係上堂做練習<br />\n冇特登死記史實同埋年份<br />\n都拎4..你自己話易唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過亦有可能因為我個老師教得好"},{"pid":"880b692f953a5a88be380c77397f4d6cd95fa9e9","tid":588224,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"History肯定係最易考<br />\nAL自修拎A"},{"pid":"3f3d29f0d416dc2be6f9e80f8b5b369d8a12363e","tid":588224,"uid":118146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"其實都唔難 只要死背同識DBQ skills 就得<br />\n最重要係不斷操essay 同 past paper <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 5* <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9419025aa31af1d5fe8252ef3a05e7e05e1b27bb","tid":588224,"uid":170967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"利申先：2016DSE 5*<br />\n<br />\n我覺得History呢科好睇你識唔識答題，資料題其實好多分都係唔洗背野輕鬆執，前提係你對啲歷史背景有基本認識，跟住你要識得組織歸納資料，做到呢啲基本上已經滿分<br />\n<br />\n長嘅sub-question同essay係要背，因為要用own knowledge，但我覺得呢一科重點係你要識揀重點背，知道有咩例子係果個topic底下99%會用到，加埋你要學識答長問答嘅基本框架，例如咩題型要反駁，trace&amp;explain又要點答，to what extent又要點答等，再加埋字速要快<br />\n<br />\n其實識讀嘅話我覺得要攞5 or above其實一兩個月乜都夠"},{"pid":"4afeaf10644c10a578fcaa02dd3c35b296834270","tid":588224,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"你讀熟歐洲<br />\n之後睇下中日嘅史料for dba<br />\n係足夠拎5**<br />\n不過dse history主要考答題技巧 <br />\n想靚grade要學哂啲skill同操卷<br />\n利申 上年dse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c313b197ec28fbd12dbe1447b63bc8867b705ab9","tid":588224,"uid":139224,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"睇你個名，樓主dental/ medic？<br />\n如果係嘅話自修history 5*對你無難度啦"},{"pid":"45bf97d85be8d343d7b31feed281a29fcfd9376c","tid":588224,"uid":69140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c313b197ec28fbd12dbe1447b63bc8867b705ab9","tid":588224,"uid":139224,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"睇你個名，樓主dental/ medic？<br />\n如果係嘅話自修history 5*對你無難度啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29308deb7292bd5f9e13398cd83c4fbc864ed267","tid":588224,"uid":144252,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"絕對可以，只要你個好老師就得，幫你私補？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054e834c9a6f523c370255aa86d9b377b092370c","tid":588224,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45bf97d85be8d343d7b31feed281a29fcfd9376c","tid":588224,"uid":69140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c313b197ec28fbd12dbe1447b63bc8867b705ab9","tid":588224,"uid":139224,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"睇你個名，樓主dental/ medic？<br />\n如果係嘅話自修history 5*對你無難度啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:58:19.000Z","ms